data.description: BACK ON MARKET DUE TO BUYER COLD FEET! WDIR and home inspection have already been completed! BRAND NEW WATER HEATER!  Welcome to this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home that offers an array of unique features and amenities that are sure to captivate. Nestled in a desirable neighborhood, this residence boasts a refreshing swimming pool, a secret passage entry to the office, a Murphy bed, two car garage, an outdoor shed, and a gas stove. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious living area that contains a wood burning fireplace and connects to the dining area, creating a space for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. One of the most intriguing features of this home is the secret passage entry to the office/bonus room. Behind a discreet door lies a hidden passage leading to a quiet workspace or game room, providing an air of mystery. Whether you work from home or simply desire a secluded area, this secret passage is sure to wow. Another highlight of this property is the delightful outdoor space. Step outside to discover your very own paradise, complete with a swimming pool and outdoor refrigerator. The yard also features an outdoor shed, providing ample storage space. In addition, the home boasts a Murphy bed, an ingenious space-saving solution that effortlessly transforms a room, allowing for versatility and flexibility. With this feature, you can easily convert a room into a guest bedroom or a home office, maximizing the functionality of your living space. Schedule your showing today!
